data.description: Hurry! Units in this subdivision very rarely come available! Great location tucked away at the back of the complex with guest parking directly across the street! Partial brick front! End unit! Private side entrance! Cozy family room with gas log fireplace, custom mantle, extra recessed lighting and plenty of natural light! Gourmet kitchen with 42" custom cabinetry, granite countertops, breakfast bar, stainless steel appliances and extra cabinets! Separate dining area with sliding glass doors to the deck and views of the tree line! Convenient 2nd floor laundry! Huge open loft with vaulted ceilings, great for 2nd living room space! Spacious master bedroom with vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet and private garden bath with new dual sink vanity, deep soaker tub and walk-in shower! Gracious size secondary bedroom! Full finished English basement with rec room, full bath and storage area! 6 panel doors! New roof! Close to shopping and transportation! Won't last!
